data.description: Nestled on a semi-secluded 2.24-acre parcel in the Mountains of Dobson, North Carolina, this recently remodeled 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom doublewide home offers a perfect blend of modern comfort and rustic charm. The newly renovated kitchen boasts new stainless steel appliances, pristine cabinets, sleek countertops, and fixtures that effortlessly harmonize with the spacious island, providing both functional space and a cozy seating area. Luxury vinyl flooring stretches throughout, offering durability and style. The bathrooms have been transformed with elegant vanities, mirrors, and fixtures, exuding a sense of opulence. Surrounded by nature's embrace, this residence is a definitely a unique retreat while still enjoying the convenience of a fresh, modern interior.
